							<h3><a href="jackson_brodie.php" title="Visit the Jackson Brodie page">Jackson Brodie</a></h3>
							<div id="jb_content">
							<img src="upld/tt/timthumb.php?src=upld/jackson_brodie/JasonIsaacs2_45223f3fbfc2.jpg&q=64&w=230&h=190&zc=1" alt="Jackson Brodie" />
							<p>Jackson Brodie is a private investigator. A former soldier and policeman he now makes his money working from investigating infidelity and finding missing cats.</p>
<p>Jackson has appeared in four of Kate Atkinson's novels. Each can be read in isolation, but are best enjoyed in order of publication:&nbsp;<em>Case Histories</em>,&nbsp;<em>One Good Turn</em>,&nbsp;<em>When Will There Be Good News?</em>,&nbsp;<em>Started Early, Took My Dog</em>.</p>
